tags.note: Most likely a service road, but needs exploring.
I think this is Lawrence Walk - or was it Lavender Walk? Need to resurvey!
Entrance to station from Grant Road - I believe there might be another one a little further west along the road. The inside of the station is not fully mapped.
This was mapped as Darien Road, but from a quick visit that seems incorrect - this part is more likely to be part of Winstanley Road. Need to resurvey carefully.
The bit touching the service road is guessed - covered by trees.
